{"tid":695384,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【新盤大戰】大角嘴利奧坊．凱岸今賣180伙 過百準買家到場","createTime":"2018-06-09T06:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T11:16:20.000Z","uid":68476,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7a253b73ae01d6b04727d2672d14fc232e638c14","tid":695384,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T06:53:10.000Z","msg":"【新盤大戰】大角嘴利奧坊．凱岸今賣180伙 過百準買家到場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180609/large/1528509447_8ce6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180609%2Flarge%2F1528509447_8ce6.jpg&h=2b6c1633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除嘉華（173）白石角嘉熙今日展開次輪銷售外，恒地（012）旗下大角嘴劏房新盤利奧坊．凱岸，今日發售首輪180伙，昨日中午12時截票，消息指共收近3,100票，超額認購約16倍。<br />\n<br />\n早上9時30分起為準買家報到時段，位於中環IFC的售樓處門外陸續出現排隊人潮，現場約有逾100人出席，場面熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n是次的入場單位為2座6樓G室，實用面積194方呎，開放式間隔，折實441.75萬元，呎價22,771元。"},{"pid":"39041ed7efeeca483c782021b9f3d80a20ec8639","tid":695384,"uid":63450,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T09:43:56.000Z","msg":"380票左右沽清了<br />\n我400號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10fa2b40b8853418355a9791bf61c21fe5f7fe37","tid":695384,"uid":171446,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T09:50:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbb51f73fc2b65b20cd8fcd4ba32edb2fa137fb2","tid":695384,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T09:51:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b23ebed187a834090f3bc1e10b3b393347a24f0","tid":695384,"uid":12241,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T09:51:44.000Z","msg":"召喚樓市淡友<br />\n大跌未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5210c715c52c68a7650daad3eccd603c7f5321e8","tid":695384,"uid":63450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10fa2b40b8853418355a9791bf61c21fe5f7f